won't give me the antidote?

87
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,800
It's so itchy!

88
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:43,760
I can't take it anymore!

89
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,200
Shame on you!

90
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,520
Give me the antidote now!

91
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,440
Beg for it.

92
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,320
In your dreams!

93
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,600
