94
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,440
Shall I scratch them for you?

95
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:53,880
You...!

96
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:55,560
You wish!

97
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:56,440
I...!

98
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:05,560
I did it

99
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,200
