125
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,120
To make you my wife.

126
00:09:25,140 --> 00:09:26,440
I don't believe you.

127
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:36,000
When I first saw you,
I was struck by your beauty.

128
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:38,800
My heart skipped a beat for you.

129
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:42,560
Then, we met again
in Jinzhou unexpectedly.

130
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,120
It was a relief to see you well.

131
00:09:48,140 --> 00:09:51,420
