167
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:33,220
♪I want to hold your hand until the end♪

168
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:37,420
♪I want to kiss your lips
till tomorrow comes♪

169
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,600
Every word I've said
is from the bottom of my heart.

170
00:11:38,980 --> 00:11:42,500
♪I want to be in your arms
and never leave♪

171
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:47,180
♪We journey through life together,
and for love, we go on adventures♪

172
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:53,620
