198
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:48,880
Greetings, Mr. Ye.

199
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,440
I'm Fu Wenyuan from Jinzhou.

200
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:51,440
I'm here to pay my respects.

201
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,600
Mr. Fu, you came from afar.

202
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:58,640
Sorry for not greeting you at the door.

203
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:00,080
Please have a seat.

204
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:03,200
Serve the tea.

205
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,160
Hey.

206
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,160
Did you not sleep well?

207
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:34,780
I'm sorry, sir.

208
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,280
I...

209
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:35,840
It's alright.

210
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:37,480
No harm done.

211
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,200
Mr. Ye,

212
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,200
if I may ask,

213
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:55,400
why does everyone here

214
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,320
seem so unsettled?

215
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:58,720
Oh,

216
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:02,520
