Ye Xiaotang.

217
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:05,480
Alas.

218
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:12,140
Just let me try one more time!

219
00:15:12,140 --> 00:15:12,840
Please,

220
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:13,680
Miss Ye!

221
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:15,240
Have mercy on me!

222
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,380
