225
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:21,360
This is torture!

226
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:23,480
What's wrong?

227
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:24,640
Why do you look so upset?

228
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,280
It's because of you, Miss.

229
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,480
