235
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:45,760
What are you doing?

236
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:49,000
Let go of me!

237
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:50,400
Let's have some fun!

238
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:51,480
Don't touch me!

239
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:55,560
Let go!

240
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:56,720
Let's have some fun!

241
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,040
Stop!

242
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:06,720
Let's go.

243
00:17:10,360 --> 00:17:11,080
What are you doing?

244
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:12,040
Help!

245
00:17:12,040 --> 00:17:12,600
Let's go!

246
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:13,560
No!

247
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:15,880
No!

248
00:17:17,120 --> 00:17:18,680
Let's have some fun together!

249
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:52,600
Miss, are you alright?

250
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:54,880
Thank you for saving me, sir.

251
00:17:57,040 --> 00:17:58,560
Thank you for saving my life, Miss!

252
00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:00,200
Get up.

253
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,320
I'm Yu. I have no one to rely on.

254
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:03,840
Please take me in, Miss!

255
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:04,760
I will be

256
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:06,760
your loyal servant!

257
00:18:07,140 --> 00:18:08,200
Get up first.

258
00:18:10,080 --> 00:18:10,840
