264
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:29,720
Is this

265
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,120
jade pendant yours?

266
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:34,440
Where did you get it?

267
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:39,640
My father bought it while traveling.

268
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,480
Do you recognize it, sir?

269
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:45,480
To be honest,

270
00:18:46,320 --> 00:18:49,080
this pendant is
an heirloom of my family.

271
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:52,600
But then...

272
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:54,720
Alas.

273
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:57,600
Can I buy it back from you

274
00:18:57,880 --> 00:18:58,760
at a higher price?

275
00:19:00,320 --> 00:19:01,040
Well...

276
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:08,000
To thank you for saving me today,

277
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:10,040
I'll give it to you as a gift.

278
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:11,120
You are

279
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,480
its original owner anyway.

280
00:19:14,040 --> 00:19:14,640
Oh...

281
00:19:21,560 --> 00:19:22,400
Miss,

282
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,360
thank you so much.

283
00:19:46,320 --> 00:19:46,920
Your Highness.

284
00:19:47,080 --> 00:19:47,800
Well done.

285
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:11,360
Sir,

286
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:12,400
what should we do now?

287
00:20:26,280 --> 00:20:27,040
No worries.

288
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,640
Let her be.

289
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:34,120
Sir.

290
