295
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,040
Your Highness.

296
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:27,400
Here is this two-fish jade pendant.

297
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:38,760
Congratulations, Your Highness!

298
00:21:58,580 --> 00:22:05,100
[Mini Story of Lu Nanyi and Lin Qingqiu]

299
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,880
Why were you holding my hand?

300
