362
00:29:06,440 --> 00:29:08,040
Should we set off the fireworks then?

363
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:10,040
Wait a little longer!

364
00:29:10,760 --> 00:29:11,200
Okay.

365
00:29:13,220 --> 00:29:13,880
